strings: This effect gives you the feeling that you are standing in a room with a complete 7.1 speaker set when using only a headphone, providing a more realistic sound experience. It should also be more comfortable and less tiring when listening to music for long periods of time.
It works with any source format from mono to 7.1.
Distance between front left speaker and listener in meters.
The delay which is introduced by the physical algorithm may sometimes be disturbing for the synchronization between lips-movement and speech. In case, turn this on to compensate.
Dolby Surround encoded streams won't be decoded before being processed by this filter. Enabling this setting is not recommended.
